âœ… Hot Reload Activated:

dotnet watch detects the change.

If eligible, it applies the update to the running application without restarting it.

ðŸ”„ If Needed:

If Hot Reload isnâ€™t possible (for example, after structural changes), dotnet watch will:
Automatically rebuild the application.
Restart the app and re-apply changes.
Youâ€™ll see confirmation in the terminal indicating that the Program.cs file was modified.

